    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Add an Image\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help plan ideas for improving the playground. Use your partner roles to work collaboratively as you prompt AI Chat.\r\n\r\n::: details [Partner A]\r\n- Write the prompt for AI Chat.\r\n- Be clear about your goal (what you want the AI to do)\r\n- After testing, listen to feedback and improve your prompt.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [Partner B]\r\n- Enter Partner A’s prompt into AI Chat.\r\n- Explain what worked and what didn’t.\r\n- Work with Partner A to suggest changes for the next prompt.\r\n:::\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Partner A, **write a prompt** that asks AI Chat to suggest some improvements to a playground. In your prompt, describe some features of a typical playground. *Don't have a prompt? That's ok! You can copy one from below the instructions.*\r\n3. Partner B, press **Send**. Explain the results to Partner A.\r\n4. **Add an image** of a playground from the Library to your prompt.\r\n5. Partner A, **write a revised prompt** that asks AI Chat for help improving the playground in the picture you've attached.\r\n3. Partner B, press **Send**.\r\n5. Partner B, then read and compare **AI Chat's responses**.\r\n7. Together, keep testing and improving your prompt to get the best response possible.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n::: details [<i class=\"fa fa-file-image-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **How do I add an image?**]\r\n- Click the button labeled **Add** below your chat input.\r\n- Choose **From Library**\r\n- Then browse the existing images.\r\n- When you have an image to upload, click the checkbox next to it to select it and then click **Attach**.\r\n- You should see the image get added to the message being sent to AI Chat.\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp\r\n\r\n:::details [<i class=\"fa fa-briefcase\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Need a starting prompt?**]\r\n>I’m a Parks and Rec worker looking for a project to improve a playground with swings, slides, and benches. Analyze this image. What are some ideas for how to improve this playground?\r\n:::\r\n",
